          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal">What is the average human reaction time?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            The average human reaction time to a visual stimulus is about 200 to 250 ms for a healthy young adult.
            Reaction time to sound is slightly faster (140–160 ms) and touch is around 150 ms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal">How is the F1 reaction time test measured?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
